sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Angular as Angular App<br/>(localhost:4200)
    participant AuthService
    participant IDS as Identity Server<br/>(localhost:5001)
    participant API as API Resource <br/> (localhost:5000)

    Note over User,API: 1. Initial App Load
    User->>Angular: Navigate to app
    Angular->>AuthService: ngOnInit() → initAuth()
    AuthService->>IDS: GET /.well-known/openid-configuration
    IDS-->>AuthService: Discovery document
    AuthService->>AuthService: Check for existing tokens
    alt No valid tokens
        AuthService-->>Angular: isDoneLoading$ = true, isAuthenticated$ = false
        Angular->>User: Show login button
    else Has valid tokens
        AuthService-->>Angular: isDoneLoading$ = true, isAuthenticated$ = true
        Angular->>User: Show protected content
    end

    Note over User,API: 2. User Clicks Login
    User->>Angular: Click "Login" button
    Angular->>AuthService: login()
    AuthService->>AuthService: Generate PKCE code_challenge
    AuthService->>IDS: Redirect to /connect/authorize<br/>?client_id=remlore_admin_app<br/>&response_type=code<br/>&scope=openid profile email ids_admin_api offline_access<br/>&redirect_uri=http://localhost:4200/auth/callback<br/>&code_challenge=...<br/>&state=/dashboard
    
    Note over User,API: 3. Authentication at IDS
    IDS->>User: Show login page
    User->>IDS: Enter credentials
    IDS->>IDS: Validate credentials
    IDS->>IDS: Check for existing authorization
    alt Consent required
        IDS->>User: Show consent page
        User->>IDS: Accept consent
    end
    IDS->>IDS: Create authorization code
    IDS->>Angular: Redirect to /auth/callback<br/>?code=xyz123&state=/dashboard

    Note over User,API: 4. Token Exchange
    Angular->>AuthService: AuthCallbackComponent → initAuth()
    AuthService->>AuthService: Extract authorization code
    AuthService->>IDS: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=authorization_code<br/>code=xyz123<br/>client_id=remlore_admin_app<br/>redirect_uri=...<br/>code_verifier=...
    IDS->>IDS: Validate code & code_verifier (PKCE)
    IDS->>IDS: Load user & create tokens
    IDS-->>AuthService: {<br/>  access_token: "eyJhbG...",<br/>  id_token: "eyJhbG...",<br/>  refresh_token: "CfDJ8...",<br/>  expires_in: 1800<br/>}
    AuthService->>AuthService: Store tokens in localStorage
    AuthService->>AuthService: Extract user claims from id_token
    AuthService-->>Angular: isAuthenticated$ = true<br/>userProfile$ = { sub, email, name, roles }
    Angular->>User: Navigate to /dashboard

    Note over User,API: 5. Making API Calls
    User->>Angular: Interact with protected page
    Angular->>API: GET /api/data
    Note over Angular,API: AuthInterceptor adds header:<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbG...
    API->>API: Validate JWT token
    API-->>Angular: Response data
    Angular->>User: Display data

    Note over User,API: 6. Token Refresh (Automatic)
    AuthService->>AuthService: Token expires in 5 minutes
    AuthService->>IDS: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token<br/>refresh_token=CfDJ8...<br/>client_id=remlore_admin_app
    IDS->>IDS: Validate refresh token
    IDS->>IDS: Load user & verify can sign in
    IDS->>IDS: Create new tokens
    IDS-->>AuthService: {<br/>  access_token: "eyJnew...",<br/>  id_token: "eyJnew...",<br/>  refresh_token: "newCfDJ...",<br/>  expires_in: 1800<br/>}
    AuthService->>AuthService: Update stored tokens
    AuthService-->>Angular: Token refreshed silently
    Note over User,Angular: User doesn't notice anything!

    Note over User,API: 7. Manual Token Refresh
    User->>Angular: Click "Refresh Token" button
    Angular->>AuthService: refreshToken()
    AuthService->>IDS: POST /connect/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token<br/>refresh_token=...
    IDS-->>AuthService: New tokens
    AuthService-->>Angular: Success notification
    Angular->>User: Show "Token refreshed ✅"

    Note over User,API: 8. Logout
    User->>Angular: Click "Logout" button
    Angular->>AuthService: logout()
    AuthService->>AuthService: Clear local tokens
    AuthService->>IDS: Redirect to /connect/endsession<br/>?id_token_hint=...<br/>&post_logout_redirect_uri=http://localhost:4200/
    IDS->>IDS: Terminate session
    IDS->>Angular: Redirect to homepage
    AuthService-->>Angular: isAuthenticated$ = false<br/>userProfile$ = null
    Angular->>User: Show login button